<h2 id="future-plans">Future plans</h2>
<p>We intend to complete the full integration of the Inria solvers with their current individual API in the Alya code so that scalability studies on different applications representative of Alya simulations can be performed (incompressible/compressible fluid, structure mechanics).
Hopefully some of them will reveal numerical or software features to be further studied.</p>

